      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained and stored in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, original state with no signs of wear. Mechanically, it is perfect, with all services up to date and documented. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that looks and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
