      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a dedicated parts car? This vehicle is in poor condition and will require some serious mechanical attention and TLC to get back on the road. It's the perfect opportunity for a talented DIYer or mechanic looking for their next big challenge at a great price!",
